15:
A crude iron heavy bowgun that,
despite its mass-produced
quality, packs quite a punch.
19:
A heavy bowgun of fine steel,
with improved durability and
power for more demanding hunts.
23:
A lavish heavy bowgun of rare
steel able to pierce even the
hardest of shells with ease.
26:
The Nergigante scales on this
heavy bowgun continually regrow,
promising unending pain to foes.
28:
Forged from Nergigante parts,
its thorns pierce the sinner's
flesh and cleanse their soul.
30:
New forging techniques have been
used to infuse this iron heavy
bowgun with elemental power.
34:
Bold yet delicate tweaks have
upped the power and element of
this elemental heavy bowgun.
38:
A heavy bowgun made of Tzitzi-
Ya-Ku parts buffed to a dazzling
gleam and honed to a razor edge.
41:
Polished to a blinding shine,
this Tzitzi-Ya-Ku heavy bowgun
emits a flash with each shot.
45:
A Legiana heavy bowgun. Fire,
and may any foe you hit shatter
amid a rain of shock-white ice.
49:
Wrapped in supple Jagras hide,
this heavy bowgun fits firmly in
the user's grip.
53:
Lavish use of butter-soft Jagras
hide makes this heavy bowgun
feel like a part of its user.
57:
A heavy bowgun wrapped in hide
tempered hard as iron in the
searing breath of an Anjanath.
60:
Jet black Anjanath hide lining
this heavy bowgun's muzzle lets
it strike in total silence.
63:
A heavy bowgun made from easily
obtainable bone. Rough-hewn, but
a sturdy friend to new hunters.
67:
Made from the densest of bones,
this heavy bowgun adds firepower
with the same ease of use.
71:
A heavy bowgun of modified bone.
The primal force of each shot
can bore through solid rock.
74:
Harnessing the power of the desert
tyrant, this heavy bowgun oppresses
enemies with its almighty power.
77:
A Diablos heavy bowgun adorned
with two proud horns. Made with
one-on-one showdowns in mind.
79:
This Black Diablos heavy bowgun
send foes flying with all the
mercy of a raging tyrant.
82:
The Pukei-Pukei's colorful down
hides potent venom, making this
a lot less cute than it looks.
86:
The venom-soaked down of the
Pukei-Pukei covering this bowgun
bristles at the sight of prey.
90:
Lavished in sharp Radobaan bone
shards, this heavy bowgun
scrapes the flesh from its prey.
93:
A bone-chilling Radobaan heavy
bowgun, enhanced for the sole
purpose of mincing quarry.
97:
Power hidden within the Dodogama
parts used to craft this heavy
bowgun grants it explosive power.
100:
The hank of white Tobi-Kadachi fur
wrapped around this heavy bowgun
is forever charged with static.
104:
The crackling shock of the Tobi-
Kadachi fur saps at this heavy
bowgun's prey bit by bit.
108:
A dragon element heavy bowgun
hewn from bone, crafted by
dark and forbidden means.
112:
A Zorah Magdaros heavy bowgun.
The muzzle resembles a volcano,
keeping a deity's wrath at bay.
115:
A heavy bowgun made from Kirin
materials whose firepower is
rivaled only by its beauty.
119:
A dragon element heavy bowgun
forged in iron, crafted by
dark and forbidden means.
122:
Beneath the beautiful exterior
of this Teostra heavy bowgun
beats a heart of searing fire.
125:
A Xeno'jiiva heavy bowgun, lord
among treasures. Its pitiless
judgment pierces all before it.
127:
A Bowgun made from Deviljho parts
that rips prey to shreds. Even its
barrel can be used as a weapon.
130:
A Kulve Taroth heavy bowgun with
unknown traits. Its true potential
has yet to be realized.
134:
A Kulve Taroth heavy bowgun
that utilizes other monster parts
for research purposes.
144:
A Kulve Taroth heavy bowgun
that possesses new properties
due to clever material utilization.
154:
A Kulve Taroth heavy bowgun that
fully harnesses the hidden power
of the materials used to create it.
158:
A hidden power seeps from
this Lunastra heavy bowgun,
as if a soul is trapped inside.
160:
This Lunastra heavy bowgun was
forged in hellfire. Sometimes
guards its user from fatal blows.
162:
This Lunastra heavy bowgun
resonates with Nergigante parts
to give a chance for regeneration.
164:
This Lunastra heavy bowgun
resonates with Xeno'jiiva parts
to help conserve ammo.
167:
A unique heavy bowgun made from
the gold of Kulve Taroth. Houses
the true might of the goddess within.
174:
Crafted specifically for the Defense
Corps, its high-performance
output is thanks to modern tech.
196:
Using only the rarest of metals,
this heavy bowgun can blow through
even the toughest defense.
200:
Receive the wages of your sin.
This Ruiner Nergigante heavy
bowgun blasts away the dark.
203:
A Nightshade Paolumu heavy
bowgun. The beautiful black fur
glistens with the blood of its foes.
206:
A heavy bowgun made from Nargacuga
parts. Its silent strikes can take
a life before the prey even realizes.
210:
Shots fired from this Tzitzi-Ya-Ku
heavy bowgun will guide the hunter
to brilliant results in battle.
213:
A heavy bowgun made from Zinogre
parts. A true monarch can push
it beyond its limits.
217:
A heavy bowgun that embodies
a Stygian Zinogre. Grants the
power to conquer heaven.
221:
Fire, and let the Shrieking
Legiana conjure a hailstorm
to shred your enemies.
226:
A heavy bowgun modeled after
a Tigrex head. It's as powerful
as it looks.
232:
Thunder roars with each shot
of this Fulgur Anjanath heavy
bowgun, shaking the very earth.
236:
A heavy bowgun made of only
the rarest bones. Powerful
enough to pierce steel.
240:
The icy shots of this Velkhana
heavy bowgun freeze the final
cries of prey in their throat.
246:
Though the color of flame, this
Coral Pukei-Pukei heavy bowgun
steals the warmth from its prey.
249:
With its added layer of thick
bones, this Radobaan heavy
bowgun mercilessly rends
the flesh from its prey.
252:
A heavy bowgun filled with
explosive Brachydios slime.
Its shots have matchless force.
255:
A heavy bowgun with the stopping
power of a Raging Brachydios.
Strong enough to crush a planet.
257:
An artisan's explosive imagination
resulted in this Dodogama heavy
bowgun with heavyweight-class power.
260:
A heavy bowgun made from
Glavenus materials. Rupture
your foes from within.
262:
The bite of this Acidic Glavenus
heavy bowgun lives up to its
imposing visage of rusted metal.
266:
Lovely but lethal, only expert
craftsmen can safely create this
Viper Tobi-Kadachi heavy bowgun.
269:
Crafted from icy sharp Barioth
parts, this heavy bowgun freezes
prey as it blasts them.
272:
A dragon element heavy bowgun
hewn from bone, crafted by dark
and forbidden means.
275:
The salvation this Shara Ishvalda
heavy bowgun offers is swift and
brutal, its mercy unremitting.
280:
The heat within this Zorah
Magdaros heavy bowgun is capable
of reducing all life to ash.
282:
Each shot from this Namielle
heavy bowgun drags its victim's
consciousness into the abyss.
286:
A terrifying Savage Deviljho heavy
bowgun stained black with the
blood of its many sacrificial victims.
288:
Each shot of this Rajang weapon
emits a shock wave loud enough
to drown out thunder.
290:
Those touched by the rage of this
Furious Rajang heavy bowgun
are instantly vaporized.
292:
An onyx heavy bowgun born from
anger and chaos. Unknown energy
flickers around the barrel.
298:
Each shot from this Brute Tigrex
heavy bowgun sends shockwaves
rippling through the environment.
300:
Bestowed upon guild knights with
stellar achievements. The sublime
glow is a source of pride.
303:
A silver Frostfang Barioth heavy
bowgun enveloped by a sharp cold.
Proof of the hoarfrost's keeper.
305:
A heavy bowgun containing the
soul of Fatalis. Sports peerless
power and performance.
315:
A heavy bowgun made from Safi'jiiva
parts. Awaken its hidden potential
by using unique materials.
